snippet.title: Little Rocketman - Full Playthrough
snippet.description: Playthrough of Miniclip's Little Rocketman. This was actually released as a paid game back in the day, though amusingly Candystand.com hosted a variation of the full version for free as Extra Jetpack Mission.
